{"about_the_game":"One day Roach invited his longtime friends, Jack, Alistair, and Magician, to visit. Jack leaned against the wall when suddenly it opened! It turned out to be a secret passage to the Mystery Chamber, and only one could enter it. Onward to adventure!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707590/extras/comic.png?t=1736560622\" /><br><br>This game is a long-standing prototype of the upcoming Mystery Chamber project, which was first released in 2015. This is the final and expanded edition of the game from the series of old games &quot;Mystery Chamber&quot;, which includes various improvements, changes in the gameplay, as well as new content.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features of this edition</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Major changes in levels and expansion of the game world compared to the original game;<br></li><li>Open world - explore each location, go back, find additional levels;<br></li><li>Many new objects that make the gameplay more diverse;<br></li><li>Almost completely redrawn graphics;<br></li><li>Original soundtrack;<br></li><li>Experience and level system;<br></li><li>Inventory - collect items that may come in handy in battle;<br></li><li>Workbench - take weapons apart, get parts from them, and use them to improve the weapons themselves;<br></li><li>Turn based battles with opponents<br></li><li>Over 70 weapons<br></li><li>Challenges - new game mode, in which you have to prove yourself somehow<br></li><li>Level Editor, in which almost all objects of the game are available;<br></li><li>Support for skins, which are created by the game's community;<br></li><li>Support for resource packs - give the game a different coloring.</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707590/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736560622","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707590/page.bg.jpg?t=1736560622","capsule